this 24-pack of versatile presets are a reflection of the past 24 months of my self-directed projects in front of and behind the lens. 

two years ago, I made the decision to stop editing every photoshoot to look identical in my feed and instead edit everything from scratch to best tell their respective stories. 

two years later, I couldn’t be happier with how each and every one of these presets turned out. I can’t wait to see how you make your life more cinematic with these 🫶🏼

as 2023 comes to an end I thought i’d share YOUR favorite self-directed photoshoots of mine from this year. it’s hard to believe I brought these photo projects and 18 others to life in just this past year. I set out on a lil side quest to shoot more this year than any year prior, and experiment creatively along the way.

i’m incredibly grateful for each and every one of you who view and support my art, as well as for those of you who collaborated with me this year. I have some exciting projects in the works that will continue to push creative boundaries in 2024, and this time around i’ll be showing the process from start to finish for each one. until then, happy new year’s 🖤
